---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="A look behind the screen ‚Äî what drives me, what I value, and what I tinker with."
  pageClass="page-red"
>
  <h1>whoami</h1>
  <p>
    The other pages cover the usual ‚Äî work, skills, projects. This one is a bit
